        Applications are invited from qualified individuals to instruct in the Human Services Certificate  Indigenous Focus program at North Island College.

 The instructional assignment involves teaching the practice course HSW 144: Indigenous Focus Human Service Practice Experience II via a blended format within a Port Alberni community agency.

